Package payroll

Class Company

java.lang.Object
payroll.Company
public class Company
extends java.lang.Object
This class defines the Company which is where all the employees work at. Company is an array class that holds the employees. There is multiple methods used to manipulate the company.
Author:
KJ Wang, Mehdi Kamal
